## Sequence (read top to bottom)

```
1. ingest:  reader → chunked → context.add (sync) OR addAsync + poll
2. query:   user request → agent → search_context tool → context.search
3. respond: tool_result merged back into the LLM call → final response
{{#if ARCHETYPE=="agent-plus-memory"}}4. memorise: memory.add(role=user) + memory.add(role=assistant) after each turn{{/if}}
{{#if ARCHETYPE=="voice-context-flywheel"}}4. post-call: webhook → ingest_transcript → context.add under ["calls", customer_id, call_id]
5. nightly: distill → delete-then-add ["calls", customer_id, "summary"]{{/if}}
{{#if ARCHETYPE=="personalized-chat"}}4. profile change: mirror to context.add under ["user", user_id, "profile"]{{/if}}
```

